### ========================================
### SUPER RADIO API - REST Client Tests
### ========================================
### Archivo principal con flujo completo de pruebas
### Para archivos específicos, ver:
### - src/features/user/user.http
### - src/features/program/program.http
### - src/features/schedule/schedule.http

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ========================================
### WORKFLOW COMPLETO
### ========================================

### PASO 1: Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### PASO 2: Login y obtener token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@superradio.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### PASO 3: Guardar token (copiar del response anterior)
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### PASO 4: Crear un programa
# @name newProgram
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Programa de Prueba",
  "description": "Descripción de prueba"
}

### PASO 5: Obtener ID del programa creado
@programId = {{newProgram.response.body.data.program.id}}

### PASO 6: Listar todos los programas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/programs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PASO 7: Crear horario para el programa
# @name newSchedule
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "programId": "{{programId}}",
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "14:00",
  "endTime": "16:00"
}

### PASO 8: Obtener ID del schedule creado
@scheduleId = {{newSchedule.response.body.data.schedule.id}}

### PASO 9: Ver la programación semanal (Ruta pública - no requiere token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule/weekly

### PASO 10: Listar todos los horarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PASO 11: Actualizar el horario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "15:00",
  "endTime": "17:00"
}

### PASO 12: Actualizar el programa
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Programa Actualizado",
  "description": "Nueva descripción"
}

### PASO 13: Eliminar el horario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/schedule/{{scheduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PASO 14: Eliminar el programa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/programs/{{programId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### QUICK TESTS - ENDPOINTS PRINCIPALES
### ========================================

### Ver perfil de usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Registrar nuevo usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test{{$randomInt}}@superradio.com",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

### Obtener programa específico (usar un ID real del seed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/programs/e84ff159-1e55-4267-8798-8e28300cddd4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### NOTAS
### ========================================
# 1. Instala la extensión "REST Client" en VS Code
# 2. Usa Ctrl+Alt+R (o Cmd+Alt+R en Mac) para ejecutar requests
# 3. Las variables con @name permiten capturar responses
# 4. Los valores {{variable}} se sustituyen automáticamente
# 5. Credenciales por defecto: admin@superradio.com / password123
